Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:19.91,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:23.44,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:23.44,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Yeah!
